-# %h3= "Welcome, #{teacher.name} from #{teacher.school.name}"
-# Displaying the first school causes confusion for teachers who are
-# in more than one school. They think that their account is locked
-# into just one school.
%h3= "Welcome, #{teacher.name}"
%p
  To get started, 
  =link_to("create a class",new_portal_clazz_path) + "."
  Once you have created your class(es) you will be able to assign 
  = t(:investigation).pluralize.capitalize
  to your students.

%p
  Your classes will be listed in the left-hand column on this page. Click on the class name to assign 
  = "#{t(:investigation).pluralize.capitalize}."

